23struct place;
24struct position {
25 double x;
26 double y;
27 position(double, double );
28 position();
29 position(const place &);
30 position &operator+=(const position &);
31 position &operator-=(const position &);
32 position &operator*=(double);
33 position &operator/=(double);
34};
35
36position operator-(const position &);
37position operator+(const position &, const position &);
38position operator-(const position &, const position &);
39position operator/(const position &, double);
40position operator*(const position &, double);
41// dot product
42double operator*(const position &, const position &);
43int operator==(const position &, const position &);
44int operator!=(const position &, const position &);
45
46double hypot(const position &a);
47
48typedef position distance;
